entry checkLogin variables string vSessionAttributes, sessionAttrList endvariables getitem/id sessionAttrList, $webinfo("WEBSERVERCONTEXT"), "SESSIONATTRIBUTES" ; Load the value of the session attributes "MyData" into the variable "value" getitem/id $username$, sessionAttrList, "UserName" putmess "checkLogin sessionAttrList = '%%sessionAttrList'" putmess "checkLogin $username$ = '%%$username$'" ;if ($username$ = "") ; return (-1) ;endif return (1) end entry initialise variables String vSessionAttributes String vUserName String vPath string menuHTMLString string vIncludedList, vRetHTML, vAdditionalParams string vItemId, vItemValue numeric vStatus string sentparameters string iSessionId string WebServerCntxt endvariables clear ;Check the session attributes for a user name. A user name logged against the ;session indicates that the user is logged in. vSessionAttributes = $item("SESSIONATTRIBUTES", $webinfo("WEBSERVERCONTEXT")) vUserName = $item("UserName", vSessionAttributes) activate $instancename.cleanState() getitem/id sentparameters, $webinfo("INPUT"), "tidp" if (sentparameters != "") REQUEST_KEY.PW_RESET_RQ/init = sentparameters retrieve/e "PW_RESET_RQ" if ($status < 0) putmess "%%$componentname - Request Key not found '%%sentparameters'" $webinfo("OUTPUT") = "Request Key was not found." return (-1) endif if (REQ_DATE + 30n < $datim) putmess "%%$componentname - Request Key expired. '%%sentparameters'" $webinfo("OUTPUT") = "Request expired. Please retry the password reset." remocc "PW_RESET_RQ" store/e "PW_RESET_RQ" commit return (-1) endif vItemId = "$tidp$" vItemValue = sentparameters $tidp$ = sentparameters putitem/id $webinfo("USERCONTEXT"), vItemId, vItemValue putmess "%%$instancename SetState (Password Reset) - USERCONTEXT(%%vItemId) = '%%vItemValue'" WebServerCntxt = $webinfo("WEBSERVERCONTEXT") getitem/id iSessionId, WebServerCntxt, "SESSION" activate "USYSSTAT".SetState(iSessionId, "GLOBAL", $webinfo("USERCONTEXT")) putitem/id $webinfo ("SESSIONCOMMANDS"), "SetAttributes" , $webinfo("USERCONTEXT") panel1 = "DSPPASSWORD" newmenuhtml = "" return (1) done endif ;if(vUserName == "") if($username$ == "") putitem/id $fieldproperties(logout.DUMMY) "HTML:Class","hidden" ;If the user isn't logged in then show the login page ; menuHtml = "" newmenuHtml = "" PANEL1 = "DSPLOGIN" else ;If the user is logged in then show the main application panel1 = "DSPEVENTS" vIncludedList= "PROFILE&uSEP;SCHEDULE&uSEP;SPEAKERS&uSEP;NEAR" call lp_build_menu(vIncludedList, vRetHTML, vStatus, vAdditionalParams) newmenuHTML = vRetHTML endif return (1) end entry lp_build_menu params string pIncludedList : IN ; list is by image/ icon HOME, PROFILE, EVENTS, SCHEDULE,SPEAKERS, NEAR string pRetHTML : OUT numeric pStatus : INOUT string pAdditionalParams : INOUT endparams variables string lsItemList string lsListItem string lsClasses numeric lnNumberOfItems endvariables ;always have at least home if (pIncludedList = "") pIncludedList = "HOME" endif ; built in order of list passed in forlist lsListItem in pIncludedList selectcase lsListItem case "HOME" lsItemList = $concat (lsItemList, "%%^%%%", "
  • Home
    • ") case "PROFILE" lsItemList = $concat (lsItemList, "%%^%%%", "
  • Profile
    • ") case "EVENTS" lsItemList = $concat (lsItemList, "%%^%%%", "
  • Events
    • ") case "SCHEDULE" lsItemList = $concat (lsItemList, "%%^%%%", "
  • Schedule
    • ") case "SPEAKERS" lsItemList = $concat (lsItemList, "%%^%%%", "
  • Speakers
    • ") case "NEAR" lsItemList = $concat (lsItemList, "%%^%%%", "
  • Near me
    • ") case "HOMELOGIN" lsItemList = $concat (lsItemList, "%%^%%%", "
  • Home
    • ") endselectcase endfor pRetHTML = $contain pREtHTML = $replace(pREtHTML, 1, "REPLACEME", lsItemList) lnNumberOfItems = $itemcount(pIncludedList) if (lnNumberOfItems = 1) lsclasses = "container b-nav text-center center col-xs-3 col-sm-2 col-md-2 col-lg-1" else lsclasses = "container b-nav text-center center col-xs-11 col-sm-8 col-md-7 col-lg-5" endif pREtHTML = $replace(pREtHTML, 1, "CLASSINFO", lsclasses) contain:blockdata+
      REPLACEME
    + end

operation cleanState variables datetime vDate endvariables
vDate = $datim - 24h ; current date and time minus 24 hours activate "USYSSTAT".CleanUpState(vDate) end
operation logout public web variables string iSessionId, WebServerCntxt string vIncludedList, vRetHTML, vAdditionalParams numeric vStatus endvariables
vIncludedList= "HOMELOGIN" call lp_build_menu(vIncludedList, vRetHTML, vStatus, vAdditionalParams)
$username$ = "" putitem/id $webinfo("WEBSERVERCONTEXT"), "SESSIONATTRIBUTES", "" WebServerCntxt = $webinfo("WEBSERVERCONTEXT") getitem/id iSessionId, WebServerCntxt, "SESSION" activate "USYSSTAT".DeleteState(iSessionId, "GLOBAL") clear panel1 = "DSPLOGOUT" menuHTML = "" newmenuHTML = vRetHTML putitem/id $fieldproperties(logout.DUMMY) "HTML:Class","hidden"
webactivate $instancename.detachInstance("DSPLOGIN")
end
operation verifyLogin public web params string varlist : in endparams
variables string vSessionAttributes string vUsername endvariables
getitem/id vSessionAttributes , $webinfo("WEBSERVERCONTEXT"), "SESSIONATTRIBUTES" getitem/id vUsername, varlist, "UserName" $username$ = vUserName putmess "DSPMAIN.verifyLogin vSessionAttributes = '%%vSessionAttributes'" putmess "DSPMAIN.verifyLogin vUsername = '%%vUsername'"
end
operation showHTML public web params string htmlToShow : IN endparams panel2 = htmlToShow end
operation speakerinfo public web variables string urlpresented, Cookie numeric presentedSpeaker numeric presentedEvent string vIncludedList, vRetHTML, vAdditionalParams numeric vStatus endvariables
vIncludedList= "PROFILE&uSEP;EVENTS&uSEP;SCHEDULE&uSEP;SPEAKERS&uSEP;NEAR" call lp_build_menu(vIncludedList, vRetHTML, vStatus, vAdditionalParams)
panel1 = "DSPSPEAKERINFO" newmenuHTML = vRetHTML
putitem/id $fieldproperties(logout.DUMMY) "HTML:Class",""
return (1) end
operation speakers public web ;scope ; input ; output ; operation DSPSPEAKERS.getdata ;endscope params string speakerid : IN endparams variables boolean vRetStatus numeric vRetCount string vIncludedList, vRetHTML, vAdditionalParams numeric vStatus endvariables
;; putmess "SPEAKERS: speakerid = '%%speakerid'" ; deleteinstance "DSPSPEAKERS" ; newinstance "DSPSPEAKERS","DSPSPEAKERS" $speaker_id$ = speakerid
if ($event_id$ > 0 & $speaker_id$ != 99999) ; speaker 999 is "n/a" i.e. is a type of session does not have a speaker
; check if event has sessions set up before loading speakers activate "EVENT_STATUS".CheckStatus("EVENT_SESSION_CHECK",$event_id$, vRetStatus, vRetCount, "")
if (vRetStatus = 0) ; no event sessions on this event panel1="DSPEVENTS"
vIncludedList= "PROFILE&uSEP;SCHEDULE&uSEP;SPEAKERS&uSEP;NEAR" call lp_build_menu(vIncludedList, vRetHTML, vStatus, vAdditionalParams) newmenuHTML = vRetHTML
activate "DSPMESSAGE".SetMessage("Info", "Event has no event sessions") return (0) else ; has event session go to speakers vIncludedList= "PROFILE&uSEP;EVENTS&uSEP;SCHEDULE&uSEP;NEAR" call lp_build_menu(vIncludedList, vRetHTML, vStatus, vAdditionalParams) panel1="DSPSPEAKERS" newmenuHTML = vRetHTML
activate "DSPSPEAKERS".getdata($event_id$, $speaker_id$)
return (1) endif else
if ($speaker_id$ = 99999) ; type of session that does not have a speaker vIncludedList= "PROFILE&uSEP;EVENTS&uSEP;SPEAKERS&uSEP;NEAR" call lp_build_menu(vIncludedList, vRetHTML, vStatus, vAdditionalParams) panel1="DSPSCHEDULE" newmenuHTML = vRetHTML activate "DSPMESSAGE".SetMessage("Info", "There is no speaker for this session") else vIncludedList= "PROFILE&uSEP;SCHEDULE&uSEP;SPEAKERS&uSEP;NEAR" call lp_build_menu(vIncludedList, vRetHTML, vStatus, vAdditionalParams) panel1="DSPEVENTS" newmenuHTML = vRetHTML activate "DSPMESSAGE".SetMessage("Info", "Please select an event to see speakers for") endif return (0) endif end
operation events public web
variables string vIncludedList, vRetHTML, vAdditionalParams numeric vStatus endvariables
vIncludedList= "PROFILE&uSEP;SCHEDULE&uSEP;SPEAKERS&uSEP;NEAR" call lp_build_menu(vIncludedList, vRetHTML, vStatus, vAdditionalParams)
panel1="DSPEVENTS" newmenuHTML = vRetHTML return (1) end
operation whatsnear public web
variables string vIncludedList, vRetHTML, vAdditionalParams numeric vStatus endvariables
vIncludedList= "PROFILE&uSEP;EVENTS&uSEP;SCHEDULE&uSEP;SPEAKERS" call lp_build_menu(vIncludedList, vRetHTML, vStatus, vAdditionalParams)
panel1="DSPWHATSNEAR" newmenuHTML = vRetHTML return (1) end
operation profile public web
variables string vIncludedList, vRetHTML, vAdditionalParams numeric vStatus endvariables
vIncludedList= "EVENTS&uSEP;SCHEDULE&uSEP;SPEAKERS&uSEP;NEAR" call lp_build_menu(vIncludedList, vRetHTML, vStatus, vAdditionalParams)
panel1="DSPPROFILE" newmenuHTML = vRetHTML return (1) end
operation schedule public web
variables string vIncludedList, vRetHTML, vAdditionalParams numeric vStatus endvariables
if ($event_id$ > 0)
vIncludedList= "PROFILE&uSEP;EVENTS&uSEP;SPEAKERS&uSEP;NEAR" call lp_build_menu(vIncludedList, vRetHTML, vStatus, vAdditionalParams)
panel1="DSPSCHEDULE" newmenuHTML = vRetHTML return (1) else
vIncludedList= "PROFILE&uSEP;SCHEDULE&uSEP;SPEAKERS&uSEP;NEAR" call lp_build_menu(vIncludedList, vRetHTML, vStatus, vAdditionalParams)
panel1="DSPEVENTS" newmenuHTML = vRetHTML activate "DSPMESSAGE".SetMessage("Info", "Please select an event to see calendar for") return (0) endif
end
operation show_application partner web
params String pPage : IN endparams
variables string vIncludedList, vRetHTML, vAdditionalParams numeric vStatus endvariables
if (pPage = "DSPREGISTER") panel1 = pPage vRetHTML = "" putitem/id $fieldproperties(logout.DUMMY) "HTML:Class","hidden" return (0) endif
if (checkLogin() < 0) pPage = "DSPLOGIN" panel1 = pPage return (0) endif
if (pPage = "") pPage = "DSPEVENTS"
selectcase pPage ; set menus, dsp in container and nav menu based on page to load
case "DSPEVENTS" vIncludedList= "PROFILE&uSEP;SCHEDULE&uSEP;SPEAKERS&uSEP;NEAR" call lp_build_menu(vIncludedList, vRetHTML, vStatus, vAdditionalParams)
putitem/id $fieldproperties(logout.DUMMY) "HTML:Class",""
case "DSPLOGIN"
vRetHTML = "" putitem/id $fieldproperties(logout.DUMMY) "HTML:Class","hidden"
case "DSPSCHEDULE"
vIncludedList= "PROFILE&uSEP;EVENTS&uSEP;SPEAKERS&uSEP;NEAR" call lp_build_menu(vIncludedList, vRetHTML, vStatus, vAdditionalParams)
putitem/id $fieldproperties(logout.DUMMY) "HTML:Class",""
endselectcase
; if (pPage != "DSPLOGIN" && pPage != "DSPREGISTER")
; putitem/id $fieldproperties(logout.DUMMY) "HTML:Class","" ; else ; putitem/id $fieldproperties(logout.DUMMY) "HTML:Class","hidden" ; endif
newmenuHTML.DUMMY = vRetHTML
panel1 = pPage return (0) ; return (1)
end
operation password_reset partner web
panel1 = "DSPPWRESET" putitem/id $fieldproperties(logout.DUMMY) "HTML:Class","hidden" return (0)
end

public web
scope output endscope
variables String vSessionAttributes String vUserName String vPath string menuHTMLString endvariables
menuHTML = $text(menuhtml)
;Check the session attributes for a user name. A user name logged against the ;session indicates that the user is logged in. vSessionAttributes = $item("SESSIONATTRIBUTES", $webinfo("WEBSERVERCONTEXT")) vUserName = $item("UserName", vSessionAttributes)
activate $instancename.cleanState()
if(vUserName == "") ;If the user isn't logged in then show the login page menuHtml = "" PANEL1 = "DSPLOGIN" else ;If the user is logged in then show the main application panel1 = "DSPEVENTS" endif return (1)
store if ($status <0) message $text(1500) ;error rollback else if ($status = 1) message $text(1723) ;no change else commit if ($status < 0) rollback else message $text(1805) ;OK endif endif endif
erase if ($status <0) message $text(1763) ;error rollback else if ($status = 1) message $text(1634) ;not allowed else message $text(1806) ;OK commit endif endif

entry checkLogin variables string vSessionAttributes, sessionAttrList endvariables
getitem/id sessionAttrList, $webinfo("WEBSERVERCONTEXT"), "SESSIONATTRIBUTES"
; Load the value of the session attributes "MyData" into the variable "value" getitem/id $username$, sessionAttrList, "UserName"
putmess "checkLogin sessionAttrList = '%%sessionAttrList'" putmess "checkLogin $username$ = '%%$username$'"
;if ($username$ = "") ; return (-1) ;endif return (1) end

#include U:zProcError ; Report an unexpected failure in a proc statement.
operation cleanState variables datetime vDate endvariables
vDate = $datim - 24h ; current date and time minus 24 hours activate "USYSSTAT".CleanUpState(vDate) end
operation logout public web variables string iSessionId, WebServerCntxt endvariables
$username$ = "" putitem/id $webinfo("WEBSERVERCONTEXT"), "SESSIONATTRIBUTES", "" WebServerCntxt = $webinfo("WEBSERVERCONTEXT") getitem/id iSessionId, WebServerCntxt, "SESSION" activate "USYSSTAT".DeleteState(iSessionId, "GLOBAL") panel1 = "DSPLOGOUT" menuHTML = "" end
operation verifyLogin public web params string varlist : in endparams
variables string vSessionAttributes string vUsername endvariables
getitem/id vSessionAttributes , $webinfo("WEBSERVERCONTEXT"), "SESSIONATTRIBUTES" getitem/id vUsername, varlist, "UserName" $username$ = vUserName putmess "DSPMAIN.verifyLogin vSessionAttributes = '%%vSessionAttributes'" putmess "DSPMAIN.verifyLogin vUsername = '%%vUsername'"
end
operation showHTML public web params string htmlToShow : IN endparams panel2 = htmlToShow end
operation speakerinfo public web variables string urlpresented, Cookie numeric presentedSpeaker numeric presentedEvent endvariables
panel1 = "DSPSPEAKERINFO" menuHTML = $text(menuhtml)
return (1) end
operation speakers public web scope output endscope params string speakerid : IN endparams
putmess "SPEAKERS: speakerid = '%%speakerid'" deleteinstance "DSPSPEAKERS" newinstance "DSPSPEAKERS","DSPSPEAKERS" $speaker_id$ = speakerid panel1="DSPSPEAKERS" menuHTML = $text(menuhtml) return (1) end
operation events public web panel1="DSPEVENTS" menuHTML = $text(menuhtml) return (1) end
operation whatsnear public web
panel1="DSPWHATSNEAR" menuHTML = $text(menuhtml) return (1) end
operation profile public web
panel1="DSPPROFILE" menuHTML = $text(menuhtml) return (1) end
operation schedule public web panel1="DSPSCHEDULE" menuHTML = $text(menuhtml) return (1) end
operation show_application partner web
params String pPage : IN endparams
if (pPage = "DSPREGISTER") panel1 = pPage return (0) endif
if (checkLogin() < 0) pPage = "DSPLOGIN" panel1 = pPage return (0) endif
if (pPage = "") pPage = "DSPEVENTS"
if (pPage != "DSPLOGIN" && pPage != "DSPREGISTER") menuHTML = $text(menuhtml) endif
panel1 = pPage return (1) end

; ; Do not change the interface of public operations since the UNIFACE component engine ; relies on these when executing entity service behavior. The implementation can be modified. ; ; Exception: the interface and implementation of public operations named uz* can be modified. ; These operations are not used by the UNIFACE component engine. ;
; ; Entity Service operations ; public (inter-component) operations are named u*. ; partner (intra-component) operations are named z*. ; More details are listed at the bottom of this trigger. ;
#define keyError = -1 #define keyNew = 0
#define keyInHitList = 1 #define keyInDatabase = 2 #define primaryKey = 1
public operation uRetr<esvEntity> ; purpose: retrieve a list of occurrences given a particular profile ; pre: first READ trigger at client component params entity <esvEntity> : OUT ; list of retrieved occurrences occurrence <esvEntity> : IN ; profile occurrence string fieldList : IN ; fields to be retrieved into <esvEntity> string where : IN ; where clause for read (only used when called explicitly) string uWhere : IN ; uWhere clause for read (only used when called explicitly) endparams variables numeric n endvariables
if (where != "" & uWhere != "") $instancehandle()->zException("uRetr<esvEntity>", "One of the parameters 'where' and 'uwhere' must be empty.") return (-1) endif
$instancehandle()->zRetrA<esvEntity>(fieldList, n, where, uWhere) ; profile occ. is unpacked and made current. Retrieve the data.
if (n >= 0) set $subsetreturn("<esvEntity>") ; data to be returned is subsetted to the just retrieved set
if ($status < 0) $instancehandle()->zProcError($procerrorcontext) return (-1) endif endif
return (n) ; data is packed and returned by UNIFACE end ; uRetr<esvEntity>
public operation uStore<esvEntity> ; purpose: indicate a store transaction (i.e. a serie of Proc statements 'write' and 'delete' at the client) ; pre: Proc statement 'store' at client component
$inStore$ = 1 end ; uStore<esvEntity>
public operation uUpd<esvEntity> ; purpose: create or update an occurrence. Similar to uRem<esvEntity> ; pre: Proc statement 'write' at client component ; uStore params string fieldList : IN ; fields to be updated occurrence <esvEntity> : IN ; source occurrence: contains key + data for update endparams variables string keyFields numeric n endvariables
if (!$inStore$) $instancehandle()->zException("uUpd<esvEntity>", "uStore must be called before uUpd.") remocc "<esvEntity>" return (-1) endif
findkey "<esvEntity>", 1 ; look-up if we already have the source occurrence in our hitlist
selectcase $status
case <keyError> $instancehandle()->zProcError($procerrorcontext) remocc "<esvEntity>" ; remove source occurrence return (-1)
case <keyNew> ; not in our hitlist, nor in database creocc "<esvEntity>"
if (n = -1) return (-1) endif
setocc "<esvEntity>", $curocc+1 ; position on source occurrence moveocc "<esvEntity>", $curocc-1, fieldList ; move data, delete source occurrence and position on target occurrence
if ($status < 0) ; move data was unsucessful $instancehandle()->zProcError($procerrorcontext) remocc "<esvEntity>" ; remove source occurrence ... setocc "<esvEntity>", $curocc-1 remocc "<esvEntity>" ; ... and remove target occurrence return (-1) endif
$occhandle()->afterCreate(n) case <keyInHitlist> ; already as target occurrence in our hitlist (position now in $result) moveocc "<esvEntity>", $result, fieldList ; move data into target occurrence
if ($status < 0) ; move unsuccessful $instancehandle()->zProcError($procerrorcontext) remocc "<esvEntity>" ; remove source occurrence return (-1) endif
$occhandle()->afterUpdate(n)
case <keyInDatabase> ; already in database, but not in our hitlist. Retrieve into hitlist and update it. keyFields = $keyfields("<esvEntity>", <primaryKey>) putlistitems/id keyFields ; copy source occurrence's primary key data into keyFields creocc "<esvEntity>" ; create profile occurrence. getlistitems/id keyFields ; paste primary key data into profile occurrence
$instancehandle()->zRetrA<esvEntity>(fieldList, n, "", "") ; retrieve target
if (n < 0) ; retrieve unsucessful, target occurrence removed remocc "<esvEntity>" ; remove source occurrence return (-1)
else setocc "<esvEntity>", $curocc+1 ; position on source occurrence moveocc "<esvEntity>", $curocc-1, fieldList ; move data from source into target, delete source and position on target
if ($status < 0) ; move unsucessful $instancehandle()->zProcError($procerrorcontext) remocc "<esvEntity>" ; remove source occurrence return (-1) endif endif
$occhandle()->afterUpdate(n)
endselectcase
return (n) end ; uUpd<esvEntity>
public operation uRem<esvEntity> ; purpose: mark an occurrence for deletion. Similar to uUpd<esvEntity> ; pre: Proc statement 'delete' at client component ; uStore ; pre: uStore params occurrence <esvEntity> : IN ; source occurrence endparams variables numeric n endvariables
if (!$inStore$)
$instancehandle()->zException("uRem<esvEntity>", "uStore<esvEntity> must be called before uRem<esvEntity>.") remocc "<esvEntity>" ; remove source occurrence return (-1) endif
findkey "<esvEntity>", 1 ; look-up target occurrence
selectcase $status
case <KeyError> $instancehandle()->zProcError($procerrorcontext) remocc "<esvEntity>" ; remove source occurrence return (-1)
case <keyNew> ; already removed - done
case <keyInHitlist> moveocc "<esvEntity>", $result, "" ; remove source and position on target
if ($status < 0) ; move unsuccessful $instancehandle()->zProcError($procerrorcontext) return (-1) endif
case <keyInDatabase> $instancehandle()->zRetrA<esvEntity>("", n, "", "") ; retrieve it for removal
if (n < 0) return (n) endif endselectcase
$occhandle()->beforeRemove(n)
if (n = 0) remocc "<esvEntity>" endif
return (n) end ; UREM<esvEntity>
public operation uEndStore ; purpose: indicate store transaction is completed, start physical store process ; pre: last Proc statement 'write' or 'delete' at client component ; uStore variables numeric n endvariables
$inStore$ = 0 $instancehandle()->zSave<esvEntity>(n) ; communicate physical write and delete to DBMS return (n) end ; uEndStore
public operation uLock<esvEntity> ; purpose: lock occurrence ; pre: Proc statement 'lock' at client component params occurrence <esvEntity> : IN ; profile occurrence to be locked endparams variables numeric n endvariables
findkey "<esvEntity>", 1 ; look-up target occurrence
selectcase $status
case <keyError> $instancehandle()->zProcError($procerrorcontext) remocc "<esvEntity>" ; remove profile occurrence return (-1)
case <keyNew> $instancehandle()->zException("uLock<esvEntity>", "Occurrence does not exist.") remocc "<esvEntity>" ; remove profile occurrence return (-1)
case <keyInHitlist> moveocc "<esvEntity>", $result, "" ; remove profile occurrence and position on occurrence to be locked if ($status < 0) $instancehandle()->zProcError($procerrorcontext) remocc "<esvEntity>" ; remove profile occurrence return (-1) endif
case <keyInDatabase> $instancehandle()->zRetrA<esvEntity>("", n, "", "") ; retrieve it into hitlist
if (n < 0) return (n) endif endselectcase
lock n = $status
if (n < 0) $instancehandle()->zProcError($procerrorcontext) endif
return (n) end ; uLock<esvEntity>
public operation uCommit ; purpose: commit transaction on ESV subtype's DBMS path ; pre: Proc statement 'commit' at client component variables numeric n endvariables
commit n = $status
if (n < 0) $instancehandle()->zProcError($procerrorcontext) endif
return (n) end ; uCommit
public operation uRollBack ; purpose: rollback transaction on ESV subtype's DBMS path ; pre: Proc statement 'rollback' at client component variables numeric n endvariables
clear rollback n = $status
if (n < 0) $instancehandle()->zProcError($procerrorcontext)
endif
return (n) end ; uRollback
public operation uzGetCollHandle ; purpose: issue a handle to the ESV entity collection, in order to ; let the client directly invoke operations on it ; pre: - ; post: if handle exists, then h contains handle, else h = "" params handle h : OUT endparams
h = $collHandle("<esvEntity>") end ; uzGetCollHandle
public operation uzGetOccHandle ; purpose: issue a handle to the ESV entity's current occurrence ; let the client directly invoke operations on it ; pre: - ; post: if occurrence exists, then h contains handle, else h = "" params handle h : OUT endparams
h = $occHandle("<esvEntity>") end ; uzGetOccHandle
; ; Partner (intra-component) operations. ;
partner operation zRetrA<esvEntity> params string fieldList : IN numeric n : OUT string where : IN string uWhere : IN endparams
if (where != "") $where$ = where elseif (uWhere != "") $uWhere$ = uWhere endif
$selectlist ("<esvEntity>") = fieldList retrieve/a "<esvEntity>" n = $status
if (n < 0) $instancehandle()->zProcError($procErrorContext) remocc "<esvEntity>" ; remove profile endif end ; zRetrA<esvEntity>
partner operation zSave<esvEntity> params numeric n : OUT endparams
store/e "<esvEntity>" n = $status
if (n < 0) $instancehandle()->zProcError($procErrorContext) endif end ; zSave<esvEntity>
partner operation zProcError ; purpose: report an unexpected failure in a Proc statement ; client: - ; pre: context contains information about $procErrorContext params string pContext : IN endparams variables string vError string vErrorDescr string vOperationName endvariables
getitem/id vError, pContext, "error" getitem/id vErrorDescr, pContext, "description" getitem/id vOperationName, pContext, "procName" putmess "Error detected by entity service %%$componentName()%%%, operation %%vOperationName%%%. %%vErrorDescr%%% (%%vError%%%)" end ; zProcError
partner operation zException params string pOperationName : IN string pErrorDescr : IN endparams
putmess "Exception detected by entity service %%$componentName()%%%, operation %%pOperationName%%% failed. %%pErrorDescr%%%" end ; zException
; ; The following protocol applies in case of cautious locking at the client component: ; Client component Server component - public operations ; ---------------- ------------------------------------ ; first READ trigger operation uRetr<esvEntity> ; lock operation uLock ; store operation uStore ; write operation uUpd<esvEntity> ; delete operation uRem<esvEntity> ; last write or delete operation uEndStore ; commit operation uCommit ; rollback operation uRollback ; ; ; Component attributes: ; $where$ where clause of read Proc statement at client component ; $uWhere$ u_where clause of read Proc statement at client component ; $inStore$ true while uStore ... uEndStore ;

; For the definition of <myDtd>, see the Defines trigger
operation deleteall params xmlstream [dtd:<myDtd>] x : INOUT numeric pError : OUT string pErrorContext : OUT endparams
pError = 0 ; initialize $procerror return value pErrorContext = "" ; initialize $procerrorcontext return value
xmlload x, "dtd:<myDtd>" ; load xml data x into component structure
if ($status >= 0) ; xmlload successful
#ifdefined ssvEntity if ($empty("<ssvEntity>") = 0) ; there is data #else if ($empty = 0) ; there is data #endif retrieve/reconnect ; fire Read Trigger for changed or deleted occurrences
if ($status = 0) ; validate successful erase
if ($status < 0) ; erase error pError = $procerror pErrorContext = $procerrorcontext rollback
elseif ($status = 0) ; erase successful commit
if ($status < 0) ; commit failed pError = $procerror pErrorContext = $procerrorcontext rollback
endif endif
else ; retrieve/reconnect failed pError = -35 putitem/id pErrorContext, "error", "-35" putitem/id pErrorContext, "component", $componentname putitem/id pErrorContext, "procname", "deleteAll()" putitem/id pErrorContext, "description", "Reconnect failed" rollback endif endif
else ; xmlload failed pError = $procerror pErrorContext = $procerrorcontext endif
; Return the result set as xmlStream to the Client.
